Detailed Description

Class describing the packet sent to the UserModule to charge a user for an operation.

After the general RequestPacket-header the format is: {tabular}{rll} Position & Size & Description \ 20 & 4 bytes & UIN\ 24 & 4 bytes & Message id\ 28 & 4 bytes & Debit info\ 32 & 4 bytes & Date in unixtime\ 36 & 4 bytes & Kind of operation (full route, list etc.)\ 40 & 4 bytes & Size of operation (Nbr SMSes or Bytes)\ 44 & 4 bytess & nbrTransactions \ 48 & ? bytes & UserOriginID to debit as string\ ? & ? bytes & ServerID as string ? & ? bytes & Description of operation as string\ & & \ {tabular}

Parameters:

requestID The id of the request.
UIN The users ID.
messageID ID of message in mc2.
debInfo MC2 debit value of this debit.
date Timestamp in unixtime\
sentSize The amout sent, number SMSes or bytes.
operationType Kind of service performed.
UserOrigin Origin of user, phoneNumber, IP.
ServerID Phonenumber of smsserver or HTTPServer IP.
operationDescription What the server did.
nbrTransactions The number of transactions to withdraw from user, default 0.
originIP The sender's IP (default = 0, set later).
originPort The port to reply to (default = 0, set later).
